Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.16,0:00:29.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(Totoro-Totoro-Totoro)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.14,0:00:33.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MY NEIGHBOR TOTORO\N{\i1}Let’s walk, let’s walk{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.40,0:00:37.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MY NEIGHBOR TOTORO\N{\i1}I’m fine{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.21,0:00:41.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}I like to walk{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.07,0:00:45.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}so let’s go on...{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.15,0:00:54.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}Hills, tunnels, grass...{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.23,0:01:02.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}bridges and bumpy gravel roads{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.27,0:01:10.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}crawling under spider webs\Nand downhill.{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.32,0:01:22.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}Let’s walk, let’s walk{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.37,0:01:25.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}I’m fine{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.03,0:01:30.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}I like to walk{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.10,0:01:33.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}so let’s go on...{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.09,0:01:38.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}Foxes and raccoons,{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.16,0:01:42.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}come out !{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.11,0:01:49.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}Let’s explore deep into the woods.{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.05,0:01:58.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}Happiness with many friends !{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.18,0:02:08.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}Happiness with many friends !{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.33,0:02:32.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Father, caramel.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.06,0:02:34.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.91,0:02:36.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Are you tired ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.16,0:02:36.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Uh - uh.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.93,0:02:38.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It’s just a little farther.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.68,0:02:48.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Oh !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.74,0:02:50.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mei ! Hide !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.76,0:02:58.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It wasn’t a policeman.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.46,0:03:00.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,HI-I-I !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.18,0:03:33.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Is someone there from this house ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.10,0:03:37.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.62,0:03:41.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I’m Kusakabe,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.18,0:03:43.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,we’ve arrived.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.24,0:03:46.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yoroshiku Onegai Shimasu\N(Thanks for your future kindness !)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.75,0:03:48.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Welcome !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.61,0:03:54.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.89,0:04:17.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Well, we’ve arrived.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.58,0:04:20.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Wait !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.78,0:04:25.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mei, there’s a bridge.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.32,0:04:26.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Bridge ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.61,0:04:32.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Fish !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.41,0:04:34.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,See, it flashed again.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.81,0:04:36.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Well, do you like it ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.17,0:04:39.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Father,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.14,0:04:41.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,it’s beautiful !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.65,0:04:43.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,A tunnel of trees !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.41,0:04:46.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ahhh..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.44,0:04:47.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,that house ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.88,0:04:53.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hurry !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.42,0:05:08.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It’s pretty old.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.45,0:05:09.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Old !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.09,0:05:11.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It’s like a haunted house !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.72,0:05:12.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ghosts ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.45,0:05:21.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It’s rotten.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.39,0:05:34.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It’ll fall down,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.98,0:05:36.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,it’ll fall down !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.70,0:05:47.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mei,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.23,0:05:48.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Look.. !\N- Huh ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.87,0:05:52.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,There...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.29,0:06:02.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Isn’t it big ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.89,0:06:03.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Achoo !...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.60,0:06:09.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Father,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.68,0:06:11.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,a huge tree !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.88,0:06:13.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Right, it’s a camphor tree.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.68,0:06:17.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- A camphor tree !\N- A camphor tree !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.77,0:06:31.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,An acorn !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.38,0:06:35.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Let me see !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.49,0:06:38.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ah, another one !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.91,0:06:45.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I have one !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.50,0:06:52.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.35,0:06:54.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We’ve got to open up\Nthe storm shutters.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.70,0:06:55.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Acorns !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.90,0:06:58.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,There are acorns in the room.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.32,0:07:00.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,They fell from above.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.36,0:07:05.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I wonder
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.98,0:07:07.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,if there are squirrels here ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.68,0:07:09.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Squirrels ?\N- Squirrels ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.05,0:07:12.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Or maybe acorn-mice ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.54,0:07:13.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.24,0:07:14.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No, squirrels are better.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.36,0:07:17.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Where do you want this ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.12,0:07:20.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ah, just a minute.\NI’ll open up over here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.34,0:07:20.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Satsuki,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.88,0:07:22.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,would you open the back door ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.31,0:07:22.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Okay.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.23,0:07:24.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-You should be able to find it.\N- Mm-hm
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.18,0:07:27.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Come on !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.88,0:07:31.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Wait !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.80,0:07:34.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hurry up !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.96,0:08:07.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,AHHHHHH !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.70,0:08:13.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- I’m going in\N- Mm-hm
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.21,0:08:27.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- The bath...\N- Mm-hm
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.36,0:08:34.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Nothing there...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.00,0:08:38.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That’s the bath.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.34,0:08:39.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Father, there’s something in here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.13,0:08:40.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Squirrels ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.07,0:08:41.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I don’t know.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.26,0:08:44.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Not cockroaches, not mice...\N...black.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.92,0:08:45.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,There were a whole bunch !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.29,0:09:00.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Well ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.42,0:09:03.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It must be "Mak-kuro Kurosuke".\N(Blackie All-Black)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.03,0:09:05.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mak-kuro Kurosuke ?\N(Blackie All-Black)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.40,0:09:06.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Like the ones in\Nthe picture book ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.62,0:09:07.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It must be...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.36,0:09:10.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ghosts wouldn’t be out\Non a beautiful day like this.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.52,0:09:18.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,When you suddenly enter a dark place\Nfrom bright sunlight...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.41,0:09:21.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,black spots appear\Nin front of your eyes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.38,0:09:22.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So that’s it !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.02,0:09:26.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MAK-KURO KUROSUKE !\NCOME ON OUT !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.35,0:09:30.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,IF YOU DON’T, WE’LL PULL YOU OUT\NBY YOUR EYEBALLS ! ! !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.19,0:09:36.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Okay, back to work.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.49,0:09:39.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Where are the stairs\Nto the second floor ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.41,0:09:44.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Let’s find the stairs and\Nopen the upstairs windows.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.56,0:09:45.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Okay !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.64,0:09:47.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mei too !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.01,0:09:57.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Toilet !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.63,0:10:00.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Over there !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.67,0:10:04.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Over there !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.61,0:10:05.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Over there !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.10,0:10:10.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Over there !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.13,0:10:10.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Over there !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.09,0:10:16.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Over there !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.38,0:10:19.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Not here !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.17,0:10:21.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Not here !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.52,0:10:33.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mei, I found it !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.16,0:10:41.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It’s pitch black.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.11,0:10:43.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mak-Kuro Kurosuke !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.87,0:10:53.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,An acorn !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.55,0:11:03.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MAK-KURO KUROSUKE,\NCOME OUT !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.73,0:11:29.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- AAAHH !\N- AAAahhhh...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.67,0:11:44.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mister Mak-Kuro Kurosuke,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.79,0:11:46.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,are you here ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.98,0:12:13.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Father !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.20,0:12:16.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,There’s something in this house\Nafter all !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.07,0:12:17.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That’s great !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.95,0:12:19.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Since Father was a boy,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.02,0:12:22.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I’ve wanted to live\Nin a haunted house !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.08,0:12:23.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ooops !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.11,0:12:26.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Oh no !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.86,0:13:13.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I got one ! !  Sis ! !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.74,0:13:28.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mei !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.45,0:13:41.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What energy !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.56,0:13:44.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Say hello to the neighbor-lady\Nwho watches over this house.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.73,0:13:46.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,She came to help us move in.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.75,0:13:48.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I’m Satsuki and this is\Nmy sister, Mei.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.85,0:13:50.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,How do you do ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.09,0:13:52.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yes, how do you do ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.00,0:13:55.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What nice children.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.61,0:13:57.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,If there had been time,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.54,0:13:59.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I could have cleaned up the house.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.42,0:14:01.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You’ve done plenty.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.17,0:14:04.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We’re so busy in the fields right now,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.54,0:14:07.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,but I cleaned a little, every so often.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.73,0:14:10.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mei, your hands are black !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.61,0:14:11.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What happened ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.55,0:14:13.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mak-kuro Kurosuke escaped !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.92,0:14:15.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Oh, Mei, your feet...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.08,0:14:22.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Oh, mine are black too !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.45,0:14:23.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Oh, ho...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.26,0:14:33.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It looks like the ‘susu-atari’\Nhave come out.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.40,0:14:34.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Susu-atari ?\N(Moving Soot)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.86,0:14:37.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Are susu-atari like this,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.00,0:14:39.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and move like this ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.72,0:14:40.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yes indeed...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.20,0:14:44.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,They breed in very old\Nempty houses,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.85,0:14:48.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and make soot and dust here and there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.36,0:14:52.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I could see them too, when I was young.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.07,0:14:56.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So, you also saw them....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.71,0:14:58.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Are they ghosts ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.97,0:15:02.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Nothing that scary.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.01,0:15:05.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,If you’re good, they\Nwon’t do anything bad.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.09,0:15:09.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Then before you know it,\Nthey’re gone.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.92,0:15:11.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,They’re probably up\Nin the ceiling right now,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.94,0:15:13.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,discussing whether to move out.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.95,0:15:21.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mei, they’re all going to leave.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.00,0:15:22.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I don’t like that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.96,0:15:25.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But what would you do\Nif they all came out at once ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.88,0:15:27.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mei not scared.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.57,0:15:28.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Okay then...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.44,0:15:31.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I won’t go with you\Nto the toilet at night.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.72,0:15:34.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Say,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.02,0:15:36.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,would you go to the creek
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.14,0:15:38.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and bring up some water ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.84,0:15:39.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The creek ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.88,0:15:41.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mei go too.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.65,0:15:45.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mei, you wait there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.96,0:15:58.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Catch any fish ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.42,0:16:11.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Granny, it works !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.73,0:16:13.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Keep pumping,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.95,0:16:16.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,until the water runs cold.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.80,0:16:18.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Okay.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.15,0:17:00.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Oh,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.89,0:17:02.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,it’s you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.21,0:17:04.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What can I do for you ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.49,0:17:06.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,From Mother,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.41,0:17:07.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,for Granny.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.18,0:17:10.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What is it ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.81,0:17:18.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Wait ! What is this ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.15,0:17:20.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Is that Kanta ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.62,0:17:24.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,YAH-H-H ! !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.40,0:17:28.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,YOUR HOUSE IS HAUNTED ! ! !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.36,0:17:30.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,KANTA !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.82,0:17:42.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Reminds me of when\NI was a boy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.71,0:17:44.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I hate boys !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.35,0:17:48.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But I love Granny’s o-hagi\N(sweet rice cake).
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.41,0:17:50.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Eat all you like.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.11,0:17:53.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Thank you for all your help.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.50,0:17:58.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.79,0:18:01.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Goodbye !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.05,0:19:18.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Father, this old house\Nwill fall down.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.11,0:19:23.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What a problem, since we just moved in.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.84,0:20:00.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Everyone laugh !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.33,0:20:02.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So your fears will all run away.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.23,0:20:06.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mei not scared.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.29,0:20:09.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mei not scared !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.15,0:20:54.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,One, two,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.23,0:20:55.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,One, two,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.35,0:20:57.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Keep it up,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.75,0:21:00.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Keep it up !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.56,0:21:07.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Okay, laundry is finished !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.70,0:21:19.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Off we go !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.55,0:21:38.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Granny !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.63,0:21:41.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Good day !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.81,0:21:43.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Don’t work too hard !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.86,0:21:46.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Where are you going ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.51,0:21:49.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,To the hospital to visit mother !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.64,0:21:52.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That’s nice !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.39,0:21:54.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Say hello for me !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.74,0:21:56.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Okay !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.46,0:22:14.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Oh, this way, this way !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.42,0:22:42.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Good day.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.43,0:22:43.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Welcome.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.45,0:22:46.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MOTHER !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.60,0:22:47.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mei,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.35,0:22:48.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,it’s good to see you !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.24,0:22:51.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Father took the wrong road.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.82,0:22:53.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Really ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.28,0:22:54.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Welcome.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.48,0:22:56.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Today is the Harvest Holiday.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.36,0:22:57.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Oh, so that’s it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.84,0:23:00.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Father’s talking with the doctor.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.58,0:23:02.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I’m so happy you all came.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.06,0:23:04.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,How’s the new house ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.67,0:23:06.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Are you settled in ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.92,0:23:11.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.78,0:23:13.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- A haunted house ?\N- Mm-hm.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.01,0:23:16.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mother, do you like\Nhaunted houses ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.31,0:23:17.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Of course.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.59,0:23:19.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I’d like to meet a ghost.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.79,0:23:21.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- That’s good. Right, Mei ?\N- Mm-hm
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.86,0:23:25.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We were worried. If Mother were scared,\Nwe wouldn’t know what to do.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.05,0:23:27.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And Satsuki and Mei ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.55,0:23:28.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I like it !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.21,0:23:29.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mei not scared !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.45,0:23:35.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Is Satsuki doing Mei’s hair ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.07,0:23:36.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.32,0:23:37.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You’re good at it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.66,0:23:39.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Isn’t that nice, Mei ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.24,0:23:42.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Uh-huh, but Sis gets really mad.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.42,0:23:44.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That’s because Mei never keeps still.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.35,0:23:45.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Satsuki,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.37,0:23:46.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,come here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.97,0:23:48.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Isn’t it too short ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.81,0:23:50.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I like it this way.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.49,0:23:53.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- Mei too, Mei too !\N- Wait your turn.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.73,0:23:56.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Unruly as always, isn’t it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.13,0:23:58.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Exactly like mine\Nwhen I was your age.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.65,0:24:02.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,When I grow up, will my hair\Nbe just like Mother’s ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.06,0:24:04.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Probably,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.46,0:24:07.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,since you’re just like\NI used to be.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.40,0:24:26.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother’s looking good, isn’t she ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.37,0:24:30.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The doctor was saying she’ll be\Nable to leave the hospital soon.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:30.95,0:24:33.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon ? Tomorrow ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.03,0:24:35.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There she goes again with ’tomorrow’.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.30,0:24:37.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow is probably too soon, though.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:37.67,0:24:40.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother says she wants to\Nsleep together with Mei again.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:40.80,0:24:43.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you’re a big girl now.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.21,0:24:45.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren’t you going to\Nsleep by yourself ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.21,0:24:47.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With mother is okay.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:08.75,0:25:10.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:10.26,0:25:12.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it’s morning !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:14.62,0:25:15.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:15.86,0:25:18.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WAKE UP ! !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:23.94,0:25:25.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I overslept again.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:25.54,0:25:27.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I’m making the bento\N(lunch boxes).
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:27.86,0:25:29.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn, I completely forgot.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:30.33,0:25:32.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s okay. I’ll make everyone’s.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:32.87,0:25:34.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s burning !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:34.10,0:25:36.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:37.69,0:25:39.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one is Mei’s.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:40.51,0:25:42.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei’s -- ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:42.44,0:25:44.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei, sit quietly and eat.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:44.35,0:25:45.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-- Yep.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:46.80,0:25:48.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Wrap it yourself, okay ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:51.66,0:25:54.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satsuki-chan !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:54.63,0:25:55.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:55.98,0:25:58.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OKAYYYY ! !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:00.26,0:26:02.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made a friend already ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:02.09,0:26:04.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She called you ’Satsuki-chan’.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:04.60,0:26:06.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her name is Mit-chan.\N( Michiko )
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:08.46,0:26:10.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gochiso-sama.\N("That was delicious -- Thank you")
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:11.52,0:26:13.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll be going.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:13.65,0:26:15.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a nice day.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:16.70,0:26:17.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,’Morning.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:17.85,0:26:18.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,’Morning.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:18.85,0:26:19.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, let’s go.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:19.60,0:26:20.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hm.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:32.49,0:26:34.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:35.13,0:26:36.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does Mei look like Sis ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:37.29,0:26:39.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hm. Where are you going\Nwith your lunch ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:39.33,0:26:41.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just over there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:03.57,0:27:05.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father, is it time for lunch ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:05.77,0:27:07.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, already ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:20.15,0:27:22.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father is a florist, okay ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:38.56,0:27:40.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tadpoles !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:59.78,0:28:01.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, bottom’s gone.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:14.58,0:28:16.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found one !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:52.55,0:33:54.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:54.28,0:33:56.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mak-Kuro Kurosuke ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:56.62,0:33:57.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To -
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:57.65,0:33:59.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To - Ro -
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:59.99,0:34:06.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To - Ro - Ro\N(Troll)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:14.95,0:34:16.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To -
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:16.20,0:34:17.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To - ro -
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:17.76,0:34:20.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To - ro - ro
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:23.66,0:34:25.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Totoro !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:25.00,0:34:27.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your name is Totoro, right ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:31.77,0:34:33.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...it’s Totoro, after all...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:36.66,0:34:38.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Totoro...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:46.01,0:35:48.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- ’Bye.\N- See you later.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:50.43,0:35:51.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m home.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:51.40,0:35:52.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:52.36,0:35:54.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is it that time already ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:54.35,0:35:56.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where’s Mei ?\NI’m going over to Mit-chan’s house.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:56.35,0:35:57.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven’t had lunch yet.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:57.86,0:35:59.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t she playing in the garden ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:59.59,0:36:01.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:01.96,0:36:03.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MEI ! ! !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:04.94,0:36:06.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:09.22,0:36:11.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:16.83,0:36:18.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:18.38,0:36:20.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found Mei’s hat.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:35.89,0:36:37.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei -- Mei ! !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:45.25,0:36:47.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MEI ! Wake up !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:48.88,0:36:51.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can’t sleep\Nin a place like this !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:53.06,0:36:55.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Where’s Totoro ?\N- Totoro ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:55.80,0:36:57.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...but...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:00.52,0:37:02.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you dreaming ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:02.47,0:37:04.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Totoro was here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:04.48,0:37:07.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean ’Tororo’ that was\Nin the picture book ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:07.49,0:37:08.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:08.51,0:37:10.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he was Totoro.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:10.77,0:37:12.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With fur...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:12.19,0:37:14.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a mouth like this.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:14.61,0:37:16.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One like this...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:16.51,0:37:18.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and one about like this...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:18.52,0:37:21.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a B-I-G-G-G one\Nlike this, sleeping !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:25.31,0:37:26.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:26.87,0:37:28.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how great !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:29.56,0:37:31.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like a secret hideaway.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:31.03,0:37:33.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father ! Mei says she met Totoro here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:34.49,0:37:36.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Totoro ? \N- Mm-hm.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:36.16,0:37:37.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:45.61,0:37:47.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:52.94,0:37:54.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:54.07,0:37:55.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nuh-uh.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:55.84,0:37:58.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before he was by a big tree.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:58.21,0:38:00.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there was only one pathway...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:00.93,0:38:03.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei -- let’s go home.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:04.03,0:38:06.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said... Mei !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:18.39,0:38:22.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s true !\NThere really was Totoro !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:22.77,0:38:24.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a lie.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:33.36,0:38:34.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:35.12,0:38:36.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It not lie.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:36.86,0:38:38.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:38.32,0:38:41.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father and Satsuki don’t\Nthink you’re a liar.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:42.53,0:38:45.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei must have met the\Nkeeper of the forest.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:46.13,0:38:48.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means good fortune is with you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:48.78,0:38:50.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can’t see him all the time.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:53.27,0:38:55.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, we haven’t offered a proper greeting yet.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:55.63,0:38:56.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Greeting ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:56.70,0:38:58.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go to Tsukamori !\N{\i1}(Shrine of Forest Gods){\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:16.29,0:39:17.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei’s gotten so heavy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:17.98,0:39:19.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father, that camphor tree.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:20.85,0:39:22.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t it huge ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:30.31,0:39:32.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:32.60,0:39:34.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- That tree ?\N -Yeah !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:34.61,0:39:36.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father, hurry. Hurry !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:47.97,0:39:50.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hole is gone.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:50.05,0:39:52.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Was this really the place ?\N- Yeah
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:53.06,0:39:55.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She says the hole is gone.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:55.12,0:39:57.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you can’t see him\Nall the time.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:57.84,0:40:00.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll see him again ?\NI want to meet him too.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:01.31,0:40:03.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if good fortune is with you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:05.45,0:40:07.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t this a beautiful tree ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:08.48,0:40:12.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since long, long ago it’s been here...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:14.35,0:40:18.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, mankind and trees were friends.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:19.38,0:40:22.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father saw this tree and\Nfell in love with that house.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:23.82,0:40:26.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sure Mother will like it too.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:26.49,0:40:29.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let’s get back home.\NWe have to eat our lunch.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:29.91,0:40:32.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah. I was supposed\Nto go to Mit-chan’s.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:32.48,0:40:34.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei go too.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:34.24,0:40:35.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:35.86,0:40:37.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for taking care of Mei.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:37.86,0:40:40.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From this moment on, ’Onegai itashimasu’\N{\i1}(We humbly beg your favor){\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:40.42,0:40:42.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onegai itashimasu.\N{\i1}(Humbly wishing for future goodwill){\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:43.50,0:40:45.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A race to the house !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:45.01,0:40:47.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Cheater !\N- Yeah !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:47.47,0:40:49.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:50.59,0:40:52.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:52.53,0:40:54.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait ! !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:56.83,0:40:59.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today I have wonderful news.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:00.09,0:41:02.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei met the spirit, Totoro.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:08.74,0:41:12.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m thinking it would be wonderful\Nto meet him too.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:42.86,0:41:43.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanta !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:43.75,0:41:46.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don’t hurry,\Nyou’ll be late !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:46.18,0:41:47.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:10.58,0:42:12.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:29.83,0:42:31.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei... ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:31.69,0:42:33.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Teacher ?\N- Yes, Satsuki ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:34.88,0:42:36.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...My younger sister...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:43.77,0:42:44.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny.. Mei... ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:45.59,0:42:48.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she says she wants\Nto go where you are,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:48.68,0:42:50.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she won’t listen.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:50.63,0:42:52.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But -- Mei !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:52.85,0:42:55.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is Father’s day\Nat the university
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:55.20,0:42:58.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you promised to be a good girl\Nand stay with Granny.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:01.18,0:43:03.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have two more hours,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:03.39,0:43:05.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Granny’s busy too.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:05.84,0:43:10.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was a good girl\Nall day, right ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:18.21,0:43:20.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny, I’ll go and speak\Nwith the teacher.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:26.49,0:43:29.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satsuki’s mother is in the hospital
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:29.36,0:43:31.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it’s rather difficult right now.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:31.23,0:43:33.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Class, we’ll do all we can\Nto help, right ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:33.51,0:43:35.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:40.84,0:43:42.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s that ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:42.41,0:43:44.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s Totoro !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:44.15,0:43:47.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shhhhh. You have to be quiet.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:47.33,0:43:48.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hm.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:01.51,0:44:03.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell them I’m going to\Nskip the club today.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:03.26,0:44:05.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I’ll tell the teacher.\NSee you later.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:05.26,0:44:07.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- See you later.\N- Bye, Bye.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:08.52,0:44:10.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei, let’s hurry ! It looks like rain.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:10.45,0:44:12.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hm !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:19.25,0:44:21.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, here it comes !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:37.86,0:44:40.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei won’t cry. Is she a big girl ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:40.07,0:44:41.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hm...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:42.76,0:44:45.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but what a problem !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:47.41,0:44:48.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jizo-san,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:48.77,0:44:51.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let us share your roof\Nfor a little while.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:34.58,0:45:35.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:56.14,0:45:58.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Good thing. Right, Sis ?\N- Mm-hm
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:59.40,0:46:01.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s got holes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:13.08,0:46:15.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father didn’t take an umbrella.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:15.74,0:46:17.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei go to meet him too.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:20.73,0:46:22.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and that’s why I forgot it !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:22.70,0:46:25.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What dummy would forget his umbrella\Nwhen it’s raining ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:26.59,0:46:28.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:28.27,0:46:30.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were probably swinging it around\Nand broke it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:30.53,0:46:32.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn’t !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:45.15,0:46:47.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:48.78,0:46:51.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Satsuki. And Mei-chan, too.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:51.10,0:46:52.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:53.94,0:46:55.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for today.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:55.54,0:46:57.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re welcome; it wasn’t much.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:57.83,0:47:00.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Kanta lent us his umbrella.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:01.09,0:47:03.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really ? That kid !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:03.31,0:47:05.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s such a beat up old umbrella.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:05.19,0:47:07.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei was with me, so it really saved us.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:07.53,0:47:09.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kanta got all wet...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:09.83,0:47:11.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:11.63,0:47:14.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s all right.\NHe’s always so dirty anyway --
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:14.66,0:47:16.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he must have gotten a little bit cleaner.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:16.75,0:47:18.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to meet your father ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:18.26,0:47:18.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:18.89,0:47:20.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How thoughtful.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:20.93,0:47:23.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Mei-chan, bye bye.\N- Bye, bye.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:33.95,0:47:35.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who came ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:35.64,0:47:37.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:41.28,0:47:43.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:56.28,0:47:58.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you getting on ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:58.87,0:48:00.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, driver.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:09.14,0:48:11.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father wasn’t on it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:11.29,0:48:13.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’ll be the next bus for sure.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:13.37,0:48:15.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does Mei want to wait\Nat Granny’s house ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:37.15,0:48:41.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(A Shinto shrine\Nto Inari-san, the fox-god)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:51.65,0:48:53.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s wrong ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:24.80,0:49:26.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:26.55,0:49:28.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sleepy ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:28.68,0:49:30.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why I told you...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:30.67,0:49:32.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go to Granny’s house now ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:34.68,0:49:37.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, it’s just a little longer...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:42.90,0:49:45.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bus is sure late...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:53.17,0:49:54.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:17.81,0:51:19.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Totoro ?...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:29.06,0:51:31.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, just a minute.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:36.50,0:51:38.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll lend you this.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:39.21,0:51:41.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, Mei will fall.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:47.70,0:51:49.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use it like this.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:06.35,0:53:08.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bus is coming.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:15.13,0:54:17.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Totoro... took father’s umbrella.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:31.80,0:54:33.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:33.55,0:54:35.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Departure. All right.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:35.54,0:54:38.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The train was late and\NI missed the bus.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:39.16,0:54:41.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you worried ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:41.30,0:54:42.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It came !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:42.03,0:54:43.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father, it came ! It came !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:43.60,0:54:45.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cat, a cat bus !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:47.41,0:54:48.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really huge !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:48.97,0:54:50.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With eyes like this !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:50.98,0:54:52.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was wonderful !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:53.99,0:54:55.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We met him, we met him !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:55.45,0:54:58.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We met Totoro !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:58.57,0:55:01.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was fantastic !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:21.35,0:55:24.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, it feels like\Nmy heart is still racing.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:25.11,0:55:28.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a fantastic, strange, wonderful day.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:29.22,0:55:32.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the gift Totoro gave us\Nwas wonderful too.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:32.61,0:55:36.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a bamboo-leaf package,\Ntied with a dragon’s whisker.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:37.10,0:55:39.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we got home, we opened it...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:39.71,0:55:42.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and inside were nuts.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:46.86,0:55:49.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If our garden became a forest,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:49.72,0:55:52.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it would be beautiful,\Nso we planted them.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:52.20,0:55:54.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... they just won’t grow.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:54.99,0:55:59.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every day, Mei says ’Still nothing,\Nthere’s still nothing’.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:00.82,0:56:04.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She’s just like the crab\Nof the monkey-crab fable.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:09.37,0:56:11.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will soon be summer vacation.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:11.43,0:56:15.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please hurry up and get well, Mother.\N-- Satsuki.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:19.16,0:56:21.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:25.34,0:56:27.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- I’m going to turn it off.\N- Wait --
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:28.14,0:56:31.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father, I wonder if they’ll\Ncome up tomorrow ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:31.22,0:56:34.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder. Totoro would probably know.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:35.05,0:56:37.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:25.05,0:57:26.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:44.23,0:57:46.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- That's where we planted the seeds.\N- Mm-hm.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:16.97,0:59:21.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray! We did it, we did it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:36.32,1:00:39.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei, we’re the wind !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:39.99,1:01:41.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no tree.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:46.41,1:01:49.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:51.53,1:01:54.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a dream\N-- but it wasn’t a dream !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:54.13,1:01:55.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a dream--
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:55.75,1:01:57.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-- but it wasn’t a dream !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:57.94,1:01:59.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:15.93,1:02:18.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kusakabe, telegram.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:20.03,1:02:22.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kusakabe,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:22.48,1:02:24.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a telegram.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:26.05,1:02:27.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody home ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:34.41,1:02:36.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:40.87,1:02:42.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:44.30,1:02:46.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one’s ready to eat.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:55.49,1:02:57.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny, this one ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:57.15,1:02:58.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s ripe.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:04.75,1:03:07.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny’s garden is like\Na treasure-hill.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:08.71,1:03:11.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, let’s take a little rest.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:17.12,1:03:19.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They’re nice and cold.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:20.25,1:03:22.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Itadakimasu.\N(Blessing: ‘I will receive’)
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:31.37,1:03:32.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s delicious !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:32.75,1:03:34.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:34.13,1:03:36.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They’ve gotten a lot of Mr. Sun,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:36.97,1:03:38.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so they’re also good for you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:38.98,1:03:40.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Mother’s sickness, too ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:40.99,1:03:42.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:42.56,1:03:46.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you eat Granny’s vegetables,\Nyou’ll get really healthy fast.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:46.37,1:03:49.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother’s coming home this Saturday.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:49.17,1:03:51.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She will sleep with Mei.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:51.88,1:03:54.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she’s finally leaving the hospital.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:54.86,1:03:57.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-uh. It’s not for good.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:57.85,1:03:59.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She’ll return to the hospital on Monday.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:59.89,1:04:01.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems they’re going to\Nrelease her gradually.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:01.75,1:04:03.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:03.20,1:04:05.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we’re going to have to\Nget her to eat more and more.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:05.84,1:04:09.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The corn Mei picked,\NMei will give to Mother.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:09.54,1:04:12.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- That will make her so happy.\N- Mm-hm !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:20.90,1:04:23.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A telegram. Nobody was home,\Nso we accepted it for you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:23.12,1:04:24.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For our house ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:28.25,1:04:31.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny, Father won’t be home until evening.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:31.25,1:04:34.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open it. It might be an emergency.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:34.28,1:04:35.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hm.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:37.60,1:04:41.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-l-e-a-s-e re-ply, shi-chi-koku-yama...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:41.72,1:04:44.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichikokuyama Hospital !\NIt’s from Mother’s Hospital !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:44.90,1:04:47.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something’s happened to Mother !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:49.06,1:04:51.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny, what shall I do ?\NWe have to answer !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:51.24,1:04:53.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, calm down.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:53.25,1:04:55.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where your father is ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:55.47,1:04:57.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know the telephone number of\Nthe research department,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:57.46,1:04:58.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we don’t have a phone.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:58.79,1:05:01.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanta, take her to your uncle’s.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:01.27,1:05:03.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Let her use the phone.\N- Mm-hm
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:08.26,1:05:10.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei, you stay with me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:20.32,1:05:22.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei, you stay with Granny !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:59.77,1:06:01.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, long distance please.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:03.32,1:06:06.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokyo 31-1382.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:07.24,1:06:08.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:09.64,1:06:12.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t she cute, Kanta ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:15.04,1:06:17.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello... Yes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:18.63,1:06:21.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, is this the\NArchaeology Research Department ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:21.03,1:06:23.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father, uh, Mr. Kusakabe please.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:24.41,1:06:27.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Satsuki Kusakabe... All right.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:30.40,1:06:32.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh Father, it’s Satsuki.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:32.60,1:06:34.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, what is it ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:35.20,1:06:36.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:37.35,1:06:39.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the hospital ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:39.61,1:06:41.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll call the hospital right away.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:41.32,1:06:44.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen with Mother ?\NWhat shall I do, Father ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:44.36,1:06:45.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t worry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:45.57,1:06:48.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as I find out what it’s all about,\NI’ll call you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:48.88,1:06:50.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask them to let you wait there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:50.96,1:06:52.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hm.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:52.22,1:06:54.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m going to hang up now.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:56.37,1:07:00.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny, may I wait here ?\NFather will call back.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:00.39,1:07:02.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. Rest awhile.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:10.10,1:07:11.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:20.95,1:07:24.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way ! This corn is for Mother.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:25.55,1:07:28.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, no way ! I’m giving this to Mother.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:44.86,1:07:47.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei, It seems Mother’s not feeling well...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:48.37,1:07:51.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so they’re delaying her home visit.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:51.58,1:07:53.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:53.91,1:07:55.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can’t be helped.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:55.27,1:07:57.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she rushes it and gets worse,\Nwhat’ll we do ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:57.88,1:07:59.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:00.62,1:08:03.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei, it’s just a short postponement.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:03.01,1:08:04.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:05.94,1:08:08.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it’s okay if Mother dies,\Nis that right ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:08.34,1:08:10.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NO !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:10.63,1:08:13.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei, you dummy ! I’m not\Ntalking to you anymore !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:24.13,1:08:25.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:28.64,1:08:31.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis is a dummy !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:59.02,1:09:02.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s put away the laundry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:03.27,1:09:06.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t be so sad, eh ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:06.04,1:09:10.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny’s come to help, so cheer up.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:13.99,1:09:18.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father’s at the hospital...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:18.87,1:09:21.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say your mother just has a cold...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:21.98,1:09:25.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She’ll be home next Saturday.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:30.02,1:09:32.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just like this last time.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:32.03,1:09:34.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a short stay at the hospital.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:34.82,1:09:36.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A little cold.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:38.06,1:09:40.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will we do if Mother dies ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:40.43,1:09:42.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Satsuki-chan...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:42.54,1:09:44.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Mother’ll...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:48.31,1:09:50.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s okay, it’s okay.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:51.42,1:09:54.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would die and leave such nice children ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:55.12,1:09:59.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t cry, don’t cry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:59.37,1:10:04.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny will be here till\Nyour father comes home, okay ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:46.84,1:10:49.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei-chan !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:54.04,1:10:56.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:59.03,1:11:00.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:04.06,1:11:05.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Mei come home ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:05.32,1:11:07.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn’t see her at the bus stop ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:07.53,1:11:08.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:09.12,1:11:10.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Funny...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:10.82,1:11:12.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...where could she have gone ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:12.72,1:11:14.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A little while ago, we had a fight.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:14.84,1:11:16.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Mei’s a...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:16.56,1:11:17.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That kid !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:17.32,1:11:19.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she went to Mother’s hospital ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:19.35,1:11:22.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Shichikokuyama Hospital ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:22.09,1:11:25.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, it would take even an adult\Nat least three hours to walk there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:25.38,1:11:26.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m going to look.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:27.83,1:11:29.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanta !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:29.46,1:11:32.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and call your father !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:32.40,1:11:35.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei-chan has disappeared !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:43.98,1:11:46.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn Mei ! She’s always getting lost.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:54.43,1:11:56.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MEI !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:03.46,1:12:05.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Mister.  Uhh...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:07.40,1:12:11.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good day. Did a little girl pass by\Non this road ? My little sister.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:12.04,1:12:14.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmmm... a little girl ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:14.88,1:12:16.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would remember if I saw someone...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:18.36,1:12:20.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it was another road ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:39.52,1:12:41.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure she came this way ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:41.81,1:12:43.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:51.71,1:12:53.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MEI !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:15.01,1:13:16.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, please !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:19.50,1:13:20.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool ! That’s dangerous !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:20.83,1:13:22.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m looking for my little sister.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:22.36,1:13:24.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see a little girl ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:24.77,1:13:26.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your little sister ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:26.07,1:13:28.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she’s on her way\Nto the Shichikokuyama Hospital.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:28.06,1:13:30.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four years old, a little girl.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:30.24,1:13:31.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryoko, did you see anyone ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:31.68,1:13:33.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-uh...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:33.16,1:13:35.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came from Shichikokuyama,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:35.51,1:13:37.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we didn’t see anyone like that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:38.38,1:13:40.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... thank you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:41.26,1:13:42.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you come from ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:42.98,1:13:44.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From Matsu-go.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:44.13,1:13:45.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsu-go ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:45.96,1:13:47.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t there some mistake ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:49.04,1:13:50.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, bye.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:01.69,1:14:03.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satsuki !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:04.75,1:14:06.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kan-chan !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:08.21,1:14:08.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find her ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:08.74,1:14:10.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. How about you ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:11.22,1:14:13.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now Dad and the others are searching.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:13.49,1:14:15.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll go to Shichikokuyama for you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:15.75,1:14:17.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go home.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:17.61,1:14:21.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei tried to get to the hospital\Nand got lost on the way, I’m sure.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:22.04,1:14:25.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satsuki, a while ago, they\Nfound a sandal in the pond.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:32.07,1:14:35.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don’t know for sure whether\Nit belongs to Mei !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:51.92,1:14:53.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find her ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:24.86,1:15:28.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Namo Amida Buddha, Namo Amida Buddha...\N{\i1}(I place my faith in Amida Buddha){\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:29.74,1:15:32.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mud’s deeper over there !\NTry there first !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:32.47,1:15:34.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, got another pole ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:43.15,1:15:45.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny, Satsuki-chan’s coming !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:50.04,1:15:51.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:52.86,1:15:54.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This...this is it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:04.00,1:16:05.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not Mei’s.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:15.89,1:16:17.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank heaven...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:17.86,1:16:21.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought for sure it was Mei-chan’s.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:21.56,1:16:23.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, Granny jumped to conclusions ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:23.52,1:16:26.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it was a mistake !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:26.20,1:16:28.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where could she have gone ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:28.79,1:16:29.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll have to start over again.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:29.75,1:16:31.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll have to hurry.\NIt’ll be dark soon.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:31.50,1:16:33.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, everyone.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:33.10,1:16:35.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s split up and search some more.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:05.29,1:17:06.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:06.80,1:17:08.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me through to Totoro’s den.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:08.50,1:17:10.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei’s lost.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:10.33,1:17:14.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’ll be dark soon -- and that kid,\Nshe’s lost somewhere.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:45.14,1:17:46.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Totoro !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:48.22,1:17:50.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Totoro, Mei’s lost !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:50.88,1:17:52.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve searched all over, but I can’t find her.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:52.78,1:17:54.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please -- find Mei.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:55.97,1:17:58.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sure she’s crying somewhere right now.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:59.47,1:18:02.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know what to do !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:00.60,1:19:02.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone can’t see it !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:54.85,1:19:56.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}’MEI’{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:13.73,1:20:17.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei-chaaannnnn....
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:25.93,1:20:28.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The trees are leaning out of the way !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:53.72,1:20:59.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(Statues of Jizo, Protector of Travelers\Nand Savior of Children){\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:59.10,1:21:01.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:04.63,1:21:06.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:08.68,1:21:10.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:21.54,1:21:22.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:22.62,1:21:24.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:27.58,1:21:28.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dummy !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:28.56,1:21:30.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:32.82,1:21:36.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted to bring that corn\Nto Mother ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:43.88,1:21:48.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}’SHICHIKOKUYAMA HOSPITAL’{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:48.24,1:21:50.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’ll take us to the hospital ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:52.62,1:21:54.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you !
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:03.11,1:22:04.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:04.60,1:22:08.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s just a little cold, and the hospital\Nhad to go and send a telegram.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:08.39,1:22:11.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The kids are sure to be worried.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:11.12,1:22:12.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They shouldn’t have done it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:12.98,1:22:15.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, the kids will be relieved\Nwhen they hear.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:15.72,1:22:18.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ve all come this far....
